casebody.data:
AGUIRRE
v.
COURTS OF WILMINGTON. No. 50P16-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 17, 2016. Rebecca Aguirre, Santa Fe, for Aguirre, Rebecca.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 12th of February 2016 by Petitioner for Petition Requesting Supervisory Control over the Inferior Courts of North Carolina by the North Carolina Supreme Court:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of March 2016."
